{"tid":202614,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇一個人陪你走過最難熬嘅時刻","createTime":"2017-04-15T15:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T19:33:58.000Z","uid":101282,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ffceca8b5777e9ecac18519380850e8dff188f1","tid":202614,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"今日對我嚟講係一個好重要嘅日子 但係今年同往年相比 我有好大嘅轉變 全因為一個人<br />\n<br />\n呢個人無怨言默默咁陪係自己身邊<br />\n最了解我 最知道我想要啲乜<br />\n雖然自己成日都好細路做埋啲on9野 <br />\n<br />\n有時我做埋啲令人感到失望嘅事<br />\n但呢個人 總係會俾機會我改過 陪我渡過一切 寧願自己辛苦啲都去接納包容自己<br />\n<br />\n又有時連你都唔明白我到底想點<br />\n但你知道我經歷過好多好多野 太多唔愉快嘅事過往都係獨自面對 令到我有好多缺陷<br />\n<br />\n直至你嘅出現 陪我去面對 我知道再難捱都有你陪係我身邊 令我人生更完整 <br />\n<br />\n每個人都會有去到樽頸位嘅時候 係 可能呢一刻你好辛苦 可能你要獨自面對 可能你覺得生存好無意義 可能你唔知為咗啲乜野去堅持<br />\n但係未來永遠有好多嘅未知之數  生命中仲有好多挑戰同障礙等你去突破同解決<br />\n<br />\n曾經嘅我 活係謊言之中 自殘企圖自殺乜都試過 諗返起都覺得自己好懦弱 但係當時嘅自己真係好無助 所有都係獨力去面對 承受一切<br />\n <br />\n我都估唔到會有呢一個人出現 會令我有咁大轉變 令我覺得人生尚會有希望 <br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴絲 呢一刻可能正正係你人生面對緊好多難關同挫折嘅時候 但係留意下身邊嘅人 你唔一定要自己去面對 仲有人會關心你 幫你 陪你一齊去渡過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有咩講出嚟會舒服啲 最起碼會有我係度聽你講 陪你捱過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最後我想多謝你呀男朋友<br />\n我愛你 我會應承你 每一日我都會成為更好嘅自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你我搵到方向 我會努力向自己嘅目標進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0648fcabcc9b68470aedc85fec0d7d670bd5404c","tid":202614,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828b9dbdf0741cd202acf4f8346a50163a7c250b","tid":202614,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"唔知你幾時睇到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825f99413b138b986413064f22739dd1884dcc1b","tid":202614,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我冇打機啦出嚟理下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e867bdd654324a77da14d381d3f084121ceb21b0","tid":202614,"uid":27391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"Sorry岩岩屌緊女無上連登<br />\n<br />\nOk收到"},{"pid":"405836b10d8f14c600840b9c0edef9c322451b13","tid":202614,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"收聲啦屌"},{"pid":"84e19b7a37ae5e39625a93ebd85a273647fdf0be","tid":202614,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:54:30.000Z","msg":"負皮"},{"pid":"ba475007b33dc99e7283596045d85708b65e73b5","tid":202614,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓上做乜鳩"},{"pid":"06fcb6ea600efdefcd30d9130789e87e7e588385","tid":202614,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"成班人無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557c5afade861fdb9d3c2ff7fb5d0625fca144d6","tid":202614,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想發放正能量姐咁都要負皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132a9172e83c63f877c586fb2e588ab4a3a94c6f","tid":202614,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:02:19.000Z","msg":"衷心咁祝福緊大家嫁<img src=\"/as